  "desc": "<p>A box for cards released by the Genius Invokation TCG Society.</p><p>Only beginners who have learned the basic rules and are verified as players can collect one.</p><p>They say that these boxes were made by researchers from the Sumeru Akademiya, and that they feature a special mechanism that can be used to detect nearby people who also possess Caskets of Tomes.</p><p>Use this function to engage in more matches against nearby players!</p>",
